Hideous Kinky;;1998;;R;;Adventure,Drama,Romance;;6.0;;Gillies MacKinnon;;Kate Winslet,Bella Riza,Saïd Taghmaoui,Carrie Mullan,Pierre Clémenti,Abigail Cruttenden,Ahmed Boulane,Sira Stampe,Amidou,Michelle Fairley,Kevin McKidd,Peter Youngblood Hills,Mohcine Barmouni,Annouar Zrika,Mohamed Cherkaoui,Abderrahim Bargache,Khaldi Cherif,Ahmed Madha;;Hideous Kinky is the story of two sisters (seven and five years old) traveling with their hippie mother from London to Morocco. They encounter many adventures, new experiences, and interesting culture as they tag along on their mother's search for freedom and love. It is told through the eyes of the youngest girl, and we learn her observations on life, Mum, and determined sister, Bea.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0136244/